name: sawlog and veneer log, azobe, debarked, measured as solid wood, import from CM | sawlog and veneer log, azobe, debarked, measured as solid wood | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/6555/documentation

This dataset represents the import of debarked azobe logs to European port.The imported Azobe trees are produced by (close to) sustainable forest management in Central Africa. The activity covers the transport to Europe.

The activity starts with the product delivered at the forest road.

This activity ends with imported Azobe wood at European harbour.
category: A:Agriculture, forestry and fishing/02:Forestry and logging/022:Logging/0220:Logging

exchanges.description: Reference product. The reference product being imported is azobe legs that are harvested from (close to) sustainable forest management in Central Africa. Data based on given reference.
